title: Ep. #83 | Catching Up: CHUNG HA (청하)
description:
Chungha stops by for a very special Halloween edition of Kpop Daebak w/ Eric Nam! Join Eric and Chungha as they discuss Chungha's most memorable collaborations, friendship with former I.O.I members, and unexpected irrational fears.
